{"tid":2222768,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣奇景百年老榕樹穿屋！","createTime":"2020-09-29T10:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T11:22:39.000Z","uid":38539,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"981c605a112edd37ccabcc34937c519486ebe589","tid":2222768,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:09:33.000Z","msg":"化市中華西路陸橋旁一棟3樓透天厝，屋主施壽容捨不得砍掉1棵百年老榕樹，46年前依榕樹生長軌跡蓋房子，大樹包覆著整棟房子，粗大樹幹也穿越廁所，形成「樹中有屋、屋中有樹」奇景。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkwPq5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkwPq5B.jpg&h=5db44afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGFD3Sj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGFD3Sj.jpg&h=2a1dba28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n施壽容46年前要蓋房子，但老榕樹就在門口，有人建議乾脆把榕樹給砍了，但他崇尚自然，認為榕樹也是有生命的，因此依循老樹生長軌跡來鋪磚塊、水泥，最後變成整棟3樓透天厝被老樹給包覆著的奇景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRdNXcn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRdNXcn.jpg&h=bbc5ea41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bXMG1D2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbXMG1D2.jpg&h=f99c4e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最特別的是，老榕樹的粗壯樹幹儼然成為支撐房子的梁柱，從1樓騎樓貫穿天花板後，直接穿越2樓的廁所，再從廁所窗戶鑽出屋外，茂密的枝幹一直延伸到3樓頂；後來，施壽容又在1樓旁種植老榕、九重葛，如今也是枝葉茂密，夏天最茂盛時，整棟房子有如被大樹給包住，這個「樹中有屋、屋中有樹」奇景消息傳開，還有民眾包遊覽車前來觀看。"},{"pid":"3d1543b580e1ebfbf78d4627e4c7365c1c5dfbd6","tid":2222768,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"會不會塌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35621b1812cc7951160b1d4758ac7cb771d2f623","tid":2222768,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"結構ok？"},{"pid":"c3fc332b193384be72fd47e6ca96f53465a53c22","tid":2222768,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSHnL4h.jpg\" d